  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read existing `RedisValidationTests.ps1`. Identify test-function pattern.</step>
    <step order="2">Add `Test-TenantPrefixInvariant` — scans Redis keys (best-effort `az redis cli keys '*'` or KEYS pattern) and verifies any non-system key matches `spaarke:tenant:...` pattern.</step>
    <step order="3">Add `Test-FailFastBehavior` — point BFF at unreachable Redis (test harness only; mock connection string); start BFF; verify startup fails with expected error message.</step>
    <step order="4">Ensure failures propagate non-zero exit code.</step>
    <step order="5">Document the additions in script header.</step>
    <step order="6">Update TASK-INDEX + current-task.</step>
  </steps>
